{"id": "1365878796938510388", "channel_id": "1365786792711819374", "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "content": "It isn't device locked, but your device does save the currently logged in account - to do what you want, you just need to login from another account in the login screen.\n\nYou can do this by clicking the little door icon on the bottom right just before you enter the game. The next time you press \"Enter Mythag\", you'll be redirected to another login screen\n\nIn your friend's case, you just need to select \"More Login Methods\" and then a \"Sign In with Steam\" option will be present.", "timestamp": "2025-04-27T02:34:41.991000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1365786792711819374", "mentions": ["452516689225973761"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1365878796603101194", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 701322, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1365786792711819374/1365878796603101194/image.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=d7951d326541deb0f9b82fa8ec5e778b99eead2508206adc2dfc791af2652a9f&"}, {"id": "1365878796955418624", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 466004, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1365786792711819374/1365878796955418624/image.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=3c26dbc9f4aa7297eec95413e74373d628a6291d0940066f9efa1da852b2bae5&"}], "reply_to": "1365786792711819374"}
